{"tid":2261651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地生報考DSE需求回升, 中五生:有了國安法不怕政治環境","createTime":"2020-10-28T13:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:41:10.000Z","uid":55700,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bb0d32cd2a1069c43390249e3b01a45e17c963","tid":2261651,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723974367747032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F2723974367747032&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=276c5d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723974367747032</a><br />\n<br />\n放棄高考，報讀香港DSE，近年成為不少內地生的選擇。 <br />\n在深圳讀DSE全日制課程的高二生Kiana：「DSE每年的考生是4至6萬人左右，但高考至少是1千萬，DSE競爭少很多，其次對於內地考生來說，理科從小就抓得嚴，讀DSE比較有優勢。」<br />\n<br />\nKiana：「我是去上學並不是去涉及政治，影響不大。」<br />\nElaine：「去年我也去了香港，目睹了理工大學那種政治氣息很嚴重的牆，到處貼滿了言論，在這種氛圍下肯定會被熏陶，但是<span class=\"red\">因為現在有國安法出來，肯定會對這種風氣有所改善，因為我是2022年去考DSE的，以後再去肯定不會有太大問題</span>。」"},{"pid":"cf2bbc16f571afa213649d8bbbe3c66907fd1651","tid":2261651,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為我是2022年去考DSE的，以後再去肯定不會有太大問題。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2022年香港會發生乜事, 都好難講"},{"pid":"52bed98b127b41e6546c023849f3cc459dc30904","tid":2261651,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"【教育機構：國際關係影響 大多衝香港而讀】 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723982744412861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F2723982744412861&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=590bfa5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723982744412861</a><br />\n鄧強光：「我期望考DSE的內地生有10多、20萬，這樣對香港非常好，無論是對就業、酒店、飲食業有很大幫助，考評局可以收很多考試費。香港出生率不停跌，<span class=\"red\">內地DSE課程對香港的老師亦是很大的就業機會。</span>」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ced8715708c8a0515d1d9bf378943f582c06a5","tid":2261651,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:15:17.000Z","msg":"香港人會去考GCSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76613cc323539445f44b4e92a2286268f64ed0a6","tid":2261651,"uid":13303,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7bb0d32cd2a1069c43390249e3b01a45e17c963","tid":2261651,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723974367747032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F2723974367747032&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7MLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=276c5d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2723974367747032</a><br />\n<br />\n放棄高考，報讀香港DSE，近年成為不少內地生的選擇。 <br />\n在深圳讀DSE全日制課程的高二生Kiana：「DSE每年的考生是4至6萬人左右，但高考至少是1千萬，DSE競爭少很多，其次對於內地考生來說，理科從小就抓得嚴，讀DSE比較有優勢。」<br />\n<br />\nKiana：「我是去上學並不是去涉及政治，影響不大。」<br />\nElaine：「去年我也去了香港，目睹了理工大學那種政治氣息很嚴重的牆，到處貼滿了言論，在這種氛圍下肯定會被熏陶，但是<span class=\"red\">因為現在有國安法出來，肯定會對這種風氣有所改善，因為我是2022年去考DSE的，以後再去肯定不會有太大問題</span>。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那周街愛黨果d係咩牆黎"},{"pid":"3a5087be4b05c70e1c911cebbb6802704f67b74f","tid":2261651,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔 : 唔要血統論, 支持民主就係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055de1a90828f75ecb9b0d770b972f4ed904f6e6","tid":2261651,"uid":56432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"蝗族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal