/>\n<br />\nKiana：「我是去上學並不是去涉及政治，影響不大。」<br />\nElaine：「去年我也去了香港，目睹了理工大學那種政治氣息很嚴重的牆，到處貼滿了言論，在這種氛圍下肯定會被熏陶，但是<span class=\"red\">因為現在有國安法出來，肯定會對這種風氣有所改善，因為我是2022年去考DSE的，以後再去肯定不會有太大問題</span>。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"內地生報讀DSE的趨勢亦吸引了不少香港人到內地教書，Venus就是其中一個。 <br />\nVenus在深圳一間學校教授通識科，她認為，在內地教通識的確有困難：「很坦白講在內地的環境，的確要經過思考的，經過一些舖敍才去表達會適合些。舉個例子反修例或佔中，當然在字眼上我們也要很小心，盡可能用一些中性的字眼，避免他們有既定的立場，也會讓他們看很多香港的新聞製作節目，譬如<span class=\"red\">鏗鏘集</span>。」 <br />\n<br />\nVenus sen sei 小心国七法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010bc49b378db73276f8060814896df1575c6085","tid":2261651,"uid":67816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"Kiana elaine學人改洋名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefb1fca55c94dd2e8969a5cebdbfb5a7088c390","tid":2261651,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"055de1a90828f75ecb9b0d770b972f4ed904f6e6","tid":2261651,"uid":56432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"蝗族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又大舉入侵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔 : 我淨係喜歡政治, 經濟資源比深圳偷有咩所謂, 深圳冇海洋法取代唔到香港架喎, 我老豆淨落層樓比我gogogo 我淨係想理政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa36addae3a4246895f203a4ce1dbfd720fa8ae","tid":2261651,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6f4f22bea39a7dd22b0622e881bdcd1be11e6173","tid":2261651,"uid":55700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7bb0d32cd2a1069c43390249e3b01a45e17c963","tid":2261651,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:10:13.000Z","msg":